{"tid":1599133,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"我成功令深藍老母變微黃！！","createTime":"2019-09-27T20:43:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-28T01:53:27.000Z","uid":285050,"like":14,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"3d1dbf4dc051c32f69bb90ef26fd9eba66621d35","tid":1599133,"uid":285050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T20:43:16.000Z","msg":"是咁的，我母親大人喺2014年雨傘運動嘅時候佢已經係一個深藍人士。呢兩三個月，經過我不斷嘅解釋，再偷偷地幫佢嘅Facebook like 左立場、有線、nowTV fan page, 佢已經成為一個微藍派。<br />\n<br />\n直至今日，<br />\n佢喺電視上聽到一個後生仔講&rdquo;裝一個免費Apps叫LIHKG&rdquo;, 佢真係照做，之後佢同我講 &ldquo;我核爆都唔割! &ldquo; &ldquo;終於有個平台可以比我了解班後生仔諗乜&rdquo; <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n咁多位，可能你阿爸阿媽係深藍，但係只要比少少耐性，佢哋會明白的！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">你細個嘅時候，佢哋一樣都係好耐心咁教你行路寫字啦！！！</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><ins>光復香港時代革命！</ins></span>"},{"pid":"a4cc15bdb4562a359cb8ccf0b539bdfe4a1354c0","tid":1599133,"uid":216279,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T20:46:04.000Z","msg":"心態要調整<br />\n求幫推 或多或少有幫助<br />\n［反省］我發現好多人都搵唔到方向及定位 入嚟啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1599090\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1599090</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"4f38e85878e6a8ddb0d90f802bc39203fe2944fb","tid":1599133,"uid":270956,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T20:51:16.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 自己屋企自己救，要俾D耐性屋企人，唔好放棄溝通"},{"pid":"d54c562c00d4aed7e1ceb6b60769fe5c9b919776","tid":1599133,"uid":37146,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T20:53:16.000Z","msg":"冇，佢地冇耐心教我寫字，係用藤條教<br />\n多謝樓主，我估之後既路我識點做"},{"pid":"5da2e355c9799c903b6f4ff56a9f79aa6886be2e","tid":1599133,"uid":63117,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-27T20:55:24.000Z","msg":"唉 我屋企果個教而不善<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bbcd3774b16a0ddbecf7af31e9fb69758a590a6","tid":1599133,"uid":51598,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"ci